# blagger

## Fetch me:

    $ git clone git://github.com/avenj/blagger.git

## Config me:

    $ vim blagger.conf

## Start me or reload on-the-fly:

    $ hypnotoad blagger

## Blag stuff using Markdown:

    $ EDITOR="vim"
    $ ./blagger blag this-new-entry

## Edit or publish pending posts:

    $ ./blagger reblag

See _examples/_ for example posts.

